Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:17.15,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.96,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Gio... Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.01,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo to robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:34.87,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoril si predsa, že ochrániš Tou, nie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.93,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty nedokážeš zachrániť Tou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.11,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zachrániť?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:48.32,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toin život je už u konca.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.19,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to hovoríš?!
