Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:06.86,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.12,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.66,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď so mnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.01,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Gio...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:18.03,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak poďme.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.93,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie! Nevydám ti Tou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.06,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhni!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:30.97,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie! Nedám Tou takému, ktorý každého zraňuje!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:36.02,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy! Neurobím to! Ochránim Tou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.63,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:49.34,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Gio, prosím ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:55.11,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toa, som jediný, kto ťa dokáže zachrániť!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:08.67,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz ťa dokážem zachrániť, keď som sa stal nástupcom Thanatosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.41,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nástupca Thanatosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.82,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to hovoríš, Gio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:26.15,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,My sme si... sľúbili, že budeme žiť spolu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:30.32,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,a že spoločne ochránime Tou, nie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.57,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak potom prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.77,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre mňa tu niet miesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:43.60,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:49.98,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieťa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:59.27,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.36,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ, tam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.70,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,T-To je čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.93,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Priblížme sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.03,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochránil si nás, Gio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.43,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Odíďme spolu, Toa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:30.30,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem to urobiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.14,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Gio...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.44,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráť sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:46.18,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Už som povedal, že pre mňa tu niet miesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:54.31,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Časom sa znovu vrátim.\N Nezabudni, čo som povedal, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.22,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:03.15,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom hovoril Gio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:07.39,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toin život je už u konca.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.26,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:15.99,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.99,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To je v poriadku, nič neurobí.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:30.26,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz je priveľmi zranená.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.35,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto dievča je Raum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:50.07,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Posledný z originálnych drakov z Thanatosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.56,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, aj ja som.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.68,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Otec...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.19,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.55,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ Sakaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:27.63,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? "Otec"? Takže...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.44,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:38.56,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:57.51,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nerob si starosti, momentálne nemám žiadne nepriateľské úmysly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.72,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Počujte, Veliteľ,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.59,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,viem, že sa aj vaša dcéra nachádzala v tom havarovanom raketopláne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:15.02,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo je s vami tento drak s podobou vašej dcéry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.52,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ona nie je moja dcéra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.36,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Je len obyčajná bábka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.00,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoríte bábka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.68,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Medzi drakmi a ľuďmi nie sú takéto putá!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.61,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zobuď sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.68,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevylihuj tu, poďme!
